name: Get Outta Here
description:
Monsters from different dimensions have invaded the Necromancer's dungeon, help him get rid of them and yeet them to the nearest open portals. 

They'll be someone's else problem.

Game created in 48 hours for the TO Game Jam 2022 by the Entwickler Team

-David Fer Piccone Valverde.

-Nicole Antoinette Taboada Marquez.
